          <article class="card card--project-compact" data-tags="recent it">
            <div class="thumb thumb--project thumb--recent thumb--heya">
              <span class="project-media-badge">Recent Project</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card__body card__body--project">
              <div class="project-header">
                <h3 class="card__title card__title--project">HEYA Limited</h3>
                <p class="project-kicker">Full-Stack Website Delivery</p>
              </div>
              <p class="muted project-summary">Built a full-stack recruitment and workforce solutions website for HEYA Limited, combining branded public pages, enquiry capture, admin-ready submissions, and a live rollout for www.heya.com.pg.</p>
              <div class="project-footer">
                <div class="project-metrics" aria-label="Project highlights">
                  <span class="project-metric"><i class="fa-solid fa-globe" aria-hidden="true"></i><span>Custom domain live</span></span>
                  <span class="project-metric"><i class="fa-solid fa-server" aria-hidden="true"></i><span>Render deployment</span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="project-actions">
                  <a href="https://www.heya.com.pg/" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Website</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div id="heya-limited-details" class="project-details" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="project-details__inner">
                  <p class="project-details__label">Configurations &amp; domain setup</p>
                  <ul class="project-functions">
                    <li>Built the public-facing HEYA Limited website on a Node, Express, and EJS stack with structured routing for services, enquiries, and branded recruitment content.</li>
                    <li>Configured persistent SQLite submissions storage so contact, vacancy, and employer enquiry data could be captured reliably in production.</li>
                    <li>Installed SendGrid-driven notification flows and business email configuration using <code>admin@heya.com.pg</code> for internal alerts and client acknowledgements.</li>
                    <li>Connected an OpenAI-powered chat assistant with environment-based configuration, request limits, and a fallback knowledge flow for safer user support.</li>
                    <li>Prepared Render deployment with Node 20+, Singapore-region hosting, automated health checks, commit-based deploys, and mounted <code>/var/data</code> storage.</li>
                    <li>Completed the custom domain and DNS setup for <code>heya.com.pg</code> and the live site at <code>www.heya.com.pg</code>.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Full Stack</span><span class="tag">Render</span><span class="tag">Cloudflare DNS</span><span class="tag">heya.com.pg</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <button
                class="project-toggle project-toggle--footer"
                type="button"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="heya-limited-details"
                aria-label="Show configurations and domain setup"
                data-show-label="Show configurations and domain setup"
                data-hide-label="Hide configurations and domain setup"
              >
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
