                <div class="project-details__inner">
                  <p class="project-details__label">Platform scope</p>
                  <ul class="project-functions">
                    <li>Delivered a live marketplace experience across product browsing, store discovery, seller handles, and individual product pages through the public marketplace routes.</li>
                    <li>Built buyer-facing flows for feed discovery, profile management, checkout, purchases, and following interactions to support a complete shopper journey.</li>
                    <li>Built seller-side onboarding and operations with store setup, template settings, dashboard tools, and order-ready storefront management.</li>
                    <li>Configured the production runtime on Node, Express, and PostgreSQL with migrations, CSRF-protected authentication, and optional Google and Facebook sign-in support.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="tags"><span class="tag">Marketplace</span><span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span><span class="tag">Buyer &amp; Seller</span><span class="tag">Live Platform</span></div>
                </div>
